In the Terraform declaration for the Ed25519 key SSM parameter:
```hcl
resource "aws_ssm_parameter" "opcert_ed25519_key" {
  name  = "/rebar/prod/opcert-ed25519-key"
  type  = "SecureString"
  value = "CHANGEME"

  lifecycle {
    ignore_changes  = [value]
    prevent_destroy = true   # <-- add this
  }
}
```

In the new variable declaration, add:
```hcl
variable "opcert_admin_principal_arns" {
  type        = list(string)
  description = "IAM principal ARNs permitted to assume rebar-opcert-admin and invoke the opcert API. Set to the operator's IAM user/role ARNs at deploy time."
  validation {
    condition     = length(var.opcert_admin_principal_arns) > 0
    error_message = "At least one principal ARN must be supplied."
  }
}
```
Document that operators supply this via `terraform.tfvars` or `-var` at apply time.
